Highlights
                    

                      

                        
M1 | karrigan's 1vs3 clutch attempt (T - pre-plant) is denied by the HE grenade of the final CT (Snappi)

                      

                      

                        
M2 | Snappi's 1vs3 clutch attempt (T - post-plant) is denied by the final CT (karrigan - 16 HP) - second half pistol round

                      

                      

                        
M2 | hades (18 HP) - 1vs2 AWP clutch (T - bomb planted after 1 clutch kill)

                      

                      

                        
M2 OT | hades - 1vs2 AWP clutch (T - post-plant situation)

                      

                      

                        
M2 OT | ropz - 1vs2 clutch (CT - post-plant situation)

                      

                      

                        
M3 | broky - 4 USP-S HS kills on the bombsite A defense (pistol round)

                      

                      

                        
M3 | karrigan - 1vs3 clutch (T - bomb planted after 2 clutch kills) to secure the map victory for FaZe

                      

                      

                        
M4 | dycha - 3 quick Deagle kills (2 HS) on the bombsite B defense

                      

                      

                        
M4 | Snappi - 1vs2 clutch (T - post-plant situation) to keep FaZe off tournament point
